<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>I get a "Zend_Json_Exception: Illegal escape sequence" exception when I execute :</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>
$input = 'abc \\uBfAe';
$encoded = Zend_Json_Encoder::encode($input);
$decoded = Zend_Json_Decoder::decode($encoded);
</code></pre>

<p>It does work when :
* I use internal PHP JSON module.
* $input has a space between \u and the rest of the text (e.g. 'abc \u BfAe').
* \u is followed by a character &gt; f (e.g. 'abc \uZfAe').</p>

